==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water dock
<hw>Wa"ter dock`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A tall,
coarse dock growing in wet places. The American water dock is <spn>Rumex
orbiculatus</spn>, the European is <spn>Rumex
Hydrolapathum</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water doctor</ent>⟦br⟧
